import React from 'react';

import logoImg from '../../assets/logo.svg';

import {
    MdDashboard,
    MdArrowDownward,
    MdArrowUpward,
    MdExitToApp
} from 'react-icons/md';

import {
    Container,
    Header,
    LogImg,
    Title,
    MenuContainer,
    MenuItemLink
} from './styles';

const Aside: React.FC = () => (
    <Container>
        <Header>
            <LogImg src={logoImg} alt="Logo Minha Carteira" />
            <Title>Minha Carteira</Title>
        </Header>

        <MenuContainer>
            <MenuItemLink href="/">
                <MdDashboard />
                Dashboard
            </MenuItemLink>

            <MenuItemLink href="/list/entry-balance">
                <MdArrowUpward />
                Entradas
            </MenuItemLink>

            <MenuItemLink href="/list/exit-balance">
                <MdArrowDownward />
                Sa√≠das
            </MenuItemLink>

            <MenuItemLink href="#">
                <MdExitToApp />
                Sair
            </MenuItemLink>
        </MenuContainer>
    </Container>
);


export default Aside;
